Set up your enviro:

mkdir ~/perllib ; cd ~/perllib
perl -Mlocal::lib=./ ; eval $(perl -Mlocal::lib=./)





lib/
lib/FungiDB
lib/FungiDB/Source - *.pm for each source
    Sources describe how to fetch data from them.
lib/FungiDB/Organism - *pm for each organism
    Organisms know their source and any special attributes about their data.